      <item>
        <title>王建民如果還在大聯盟他綽號會是啥??</title>
        <description>&lt;figure&gt;
&lt;img src=&quot;http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170331/640_27ea0e0b97df825fbccc3927dfa37f8e.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;
